    "body": "Btw If you want to deploy the `checkpoint oracle` for your own private network, you can use tool `checkpoint-admin` https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/tree/master/cmd/checkpoint-admin.\r\n\r\nStep:\r\n* Deploy a checkpoint oracle via `checkpoint-admin`\r\n* Add the oracle information(e.g. `address`, `signers`, `threshold`) to config file\r\n* Use `checkpoint-admin` to sign and publish some latest checkpoint",
